WEBVTT

00:03:31.791 --> 00:03:33.663
has the opportunity to earn a living

00:03:34.228 --> 00:03:36.402
by collecting material from door to door,

00:03:37.720 --> 00:03:39.180
from the streets,

00:03:39.204 --> 00:03:40.585
from business to business.

00:03:42.363 --> 00:03:45.675
And at the end of her day,
she gets to bring the material back to us,

00:03:46.236 --> 00:03:48.537
where we weigh it,
we check it for quality,

00:03:48.934 --> 00:03:51.561
and we transfer the value
into her account.

00:03:55.704 --> 00:03:57.704
Lise now has a steady,

00:03:58.386 --> 00:04:00.569
reliable source of income.